;:1361772034,&quot;video&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:200067,&quot;status&quot;:&quot;successful&quot;,&quot;high&quot;:&quot;https://d2pq0u4uni88oo.cloudfront.net/projects/417010/video-200067-h264_high.mp4?2013&quot;,&quot;base&quot;:&quot;https://d2pq0u4uni88oo.cloudfront.net/projects/417010/video-200067-h264_base.mp4?2013&quot;,&quot;webm&quot;:&quot;https://d2pq0u4uni88oo.cloudfront.net/projects/417010/video-200067-webm.webm?2013&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:640,&quot;height&quot;:360,&quot;frame&quot;:&quot;https://d2pq0u4uni88oo.cloudfront.net/projects/417010/video-200067-h264_base.jpg?2013&quot;},&quot;comments_count&quot;:22,&quot;updates_count&quot;:3,&quot;rewards&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:0,&quot;minimum&quot;:1,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;No Reward&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:1317442,&quot;minimum&quot;:5.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;A big thank you from us! We absolutely appreciate every dollar we can get to help make this happen.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:false,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1359676800,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:31,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1390104312},{&quot;id&quot;:1317443,&quot;minimum&quot;:10.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;Your name or company name and a website link of your choice (with our approval) will be listed on the sponsors section of our website.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:false,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1359676800,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:51,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1392362650},{&quot;id&quot;:1317373,&quot;minimum&quot;:25.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You will receive all the previous levels plus a digital download of all our project videos including simulations, testing videos, flight videos etc. as well as exclusive videos never published publicly in DVD ISO format, so that you can burn a copy and watch it in your own DVD player.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:false,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1385856000,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:29,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1386747347},{&quot;id&quot;:1317374,&quot;minimum&quot;:30.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You will receive all the previous levels plus a physical DVD copy of all our project videos including simulations, testing videos, flight videos etc. The DVD will include a traditional DVD case with cover art and special sponsor recognitions.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:true,&quot;shipping&quot;:&quot;international&quot;,&quot;shipping_amount&quot;:&quot;7.0&quot;,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1385856000,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:10,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1361772976},{&quot;id&quot;:1285661,&quot;minimum&quot;:40.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You get a t-shirt! We will be creating several t-shirt designs and allowing supporters to vote for their favorites. The best 2 designs will be printed and shipped to you based on your design and size preference. These shirts will also be EXCLUSIVELY for Kickstarter backers. We will not make them available for purchase anywhere else.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:true,&quot;shipping&quot;:&quot;domestic&quot;,&quot;shipping_amount&quot;:&quot;0.0&quot;,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1367366400,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:16,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1361772973},{&quot;id&quot;:1363891,&quot;minimum&quot;:40.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;Whoops! We forgot to make the t-shirt reward available internationally. Use this reward level for internationally shipped t-shirts! From the original reward: You get a t-shirt! We will be creating several t-shirt designs and allowing supporters to vote for their favorites. The best 2 designs will be printed and shipped to you based on your design and size preference. These shirts will also be EXCLUSIVELY for Kickstarter backers. We will not make them available for purchase anywhere else.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:true,&quot;shipping&quot;:&quot;international&quot;,&quot;shipping_amount&quot;:&quot;10.0&quot;,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1367366400,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:1,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1361804925},{&quot;id&quot;:1319225,&quot;minimum&quot;:60.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You will receive the $10, $30 and $40 levels. That&#39;s recognition on our website, a DVD of all our videos, and a T-Shirt!&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:true,&quot;shipping&quot;:&quot;international&quot;,&quot;shipping_amount&quot;:&quot;10.0&quot;,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1375315200,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:11,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1362380414},{&quot;id&quot;:1317607,&quot;minimum&quot;:75.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;We will test and compile lift and torque data on a set of 5 helicopter main rotor blades for the first 20 contributors at this level.For every 10 additional contributors, we will add a set of blades to be tested. All contributors at this level will be able to recommend and vote for the blades that will be tested. The report will be delivered digitally in PDF format.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:false,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1377993600,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:4,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1361772963},{&quot;id&quot;:1265660,&quot;minimum&quot;:250.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You will receive all of the above plus a bound hard copy of the final report, drawings of all parts and assemblies, bill of materials, and complete source code; Basically, every piece of information you would need to build your own HLQ.&quot;,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:true,&quot;shipping&quot;:&quot;international&quot;,&quot;shipping_amount&quot;:&quot;20.0&quot;,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1370044800,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;backers_count&quot;:11,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1362114695},{&quot;id&quot;:1317427,&quot;minimum&quot;:300.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You will receive an exclusive invite to a HLQ demonstration viewing party. We will demonstrate HLQ&#39;s capabilities and want you to see it! The viewing location and date is yet to be determined, but will be around the end of May or beginning of June, and in the greater San Francisco Bay Area.&quot;,&quot;limit&quot;:10,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:false,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1372636800,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;remaining&quot;:9,&quot;backers_count&quot;:1,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1361772963},{&quot;id&quot;:1265661,&quot;minimum&quot;:500.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You are a super sponsor! You will receive the t-shirt, DVD, and an invite to the demonstration viewing party. At this reward level you or your company will also be featured as a sponsor on our website. A logo of your choice (and as approved by us) will be prominently displayed and linked at the top of the sponsors page of the HLQ website and at the end of every video or presentation the project produces once the project is funded.&quot;,&quot;limit&quot;:6,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:false,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1359676800,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;remaining&quot;:3,&quot;backers_count&quot;:3,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1361772966},{&quot;id&quot;:1319729,&quot;minimum&quot;:1000.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;You are a super-duper-sponsor! You will receive the t-shirt, DVD, and an invite to the demonstration viewing party. At this reward level you or your company will also be featured as a sponsor on our website. A logo of your choice (and as approved by us) will be prominently displayed and linked on the FRONT PAGE of the HLQ website and at the BEGINNING of every video or presentation the project produces once the project is funded.&quot;,&quot;limit&quot;:4,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:false,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1359676800,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;remaining&quot;:3,&quot;backers_count&quot;:1,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1361805500},{&quot;id&quot;:1317608,&quot;minimum&quot;:10000.0,&quot;reward&quot;:&quot;Once the project is completed and all features developed, you will be the proud owner of your very own Heavy Lift Quadcopter prototype! We will show you how to maintain and operate it as well as provide you with support. Please remember, the prototype will still be a development model. While we have and will be putting our greatest effort into designing HLQ with overview from experienced professionals, we cannot warrant against design or manufacturing defects. We also will need to test and demo HLQ. If it were to have a failure, there is a possibility that it could be catastrophic, and irreparable. You will still receive HLQ in this event, but as-is, and if you still want it. Rest assured, however, that it is also in our best interest to keep HLQ always operating safely, and we will do our best to keep it so. You will also receive the t-shirt, DVD, documentation package, and an invite to the demonstration viewing party.&quot;,&quot;limit&quot;:1,&quot;shipping_applicable&quot;:true,&quot;shipping&quot;:&quot;domestic&quot;,&quot;shipping_amount&quot;:&quot;0.0&quot;,&quot;estimated_delivery_on&quot;:1401580800,&quot;project_id&quot;:35462510,&quot;remaining&quot;:1,&quot;backers_count&quot;:0,&quot;updated_at&quot;:1359010892}]}";\n  //]]>\n</script>\n\n<script>\n  //<![CDATA[\n    window.current_ip = ''114.32.175.163'';\n    window.current_ip_datacenter = ''false'';\n    window.enabled_features = {"backerhistory":true,"elasticsearch":true,"advanced_discovery_es":true,"ios_crashlytics":true,"ios_mixpanel":true,"password_reset_banner":true}\n  //]]>\n</script>\n\n<script>\n  //<![CDATA[\n    var _sf_startpt=(new Date()).getTime();\n    docElement = this.document.documentElement;\n    docElement.className=docElement.className.replace(/\\bno-js\\b/,'''') + ''js'';\n    \n    window.timeRemaining = function timeRemaining(epochTime){\n    \n      var diff = epochTime - ((new Date()).getTime() / 1000);\n      var num_unit = (diff < 60 && [Math.max(diff, 0), ''