body clearfix">\r\n   <div class="avatar">\r\n      <img alt='''' src=''http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6c5e7c8e97eecc002b1d277219854fbb?s=73&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D73&amp;r=G'' class=''avatar avatar-73 photo'' height=''73'' width=''73'' />      <span class="overlay"></span>\r\n   </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class="comment-wrap">\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-author vcard">\r\n        <span class="fn">造假</span>      </div>\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.dearjohn.idv.tw/1325/comment-page-1#comment-60087937">2014 年 02 月 16 日</a></div>\r\n      \r\n            \r\n      <div class="comment-content"><p>這篇文章約12年前就在ptt上出現過了，應該是華人寫的假文章。<br />\n從沒有人能舉出原文（當然，因為是造假的）</p>\n</div> <!-- end comment-content-->\r\n     <div class="reply-container"><a class=''comment-reply-link'' href=''/1325?replytocom=60087937#respond'' onclick=''return addComment.moveForm("comment-60087937", "60087937", "respond", "1325")''>Reply</a></div>   </div> <!-- end comment-wrap-->  \r\n </div> <!-- end comment-body-->\r\n \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n    <li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-60087892">\r\n    \r\n      <div class="entry post entry-full">\r\n     <div class="border">\r\n        <div class="bottom">\r\n          <div class="entry-content clearfix">\r\n  \r\n  <div id="comment-60087892" class="comment-body clearfix">\r\n   <div class="avatar">\r\n      <img alt='''' src=''http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/40768981c6f57e6fa271029c433b3323?s=73&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D73&amp;r=G'' class=''avatar avatar-73 photo'' height=''73'' width=''73'' />      <span class="overlay"></span>\r\n   </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class="comment-wrap">\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-author vcard">\r\n        <span class="fn"><a href=''http://lkksdgod.blogspot.com'' rel=''external nofollow'' class=''url''>臺語是客家話</a></span>     </div>\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.dearjohn.idv.tw/1325/comment-page-1#comment-60087892">2014 年 02 月 14 日</a></div>\r\n      \r\n            \r\n      <div class="comment-content"><p>所以這是文化差異啊  <img src="http://www.dearjohn.idv.tw/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>\n</div> <!-- end comment-content-->\r\n     <div class="reply-container"><a class=''comment-reply-link'' href=''/1325?replytocom=60087892#respond'' onclick=''return addComment.moveForm("comment-60087892", "60087892", "respond", "1325")''>Reply</a></div>   </div> <!-- end comment-wrap-->  \r\n </div> <!-- end comment-body-->\r\n \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n    <li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-60087830">\r\n    \r\n     <div class="entry post entry-full">\r\n     <div class="border">\r\n        <div class="bottom">\r\n          <div class="entry-content clearfix">\r\n  \r\n  <div id="comment-60087830" class="comment-body clearfix">\r\n   <div class="avatar">\r\n      <img alt='''' src=''http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/9ce1b6ad24953f754e818af1cc9b657a?s=73&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D73&amp;r=G'' class=''avatar avatar-73 photo'' height=''73'' width=''73'' />      <span class="overlay"></span>\r\n   </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class="comment-wrap">\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-author vcard">\r\n        <span class="fn">神鵰俠侶的粉絲</span>     </div>\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.dearjohn.idv.tw/1325/comment-page-1#comment-60087830">2014 年 02 月 12 日</a></div>\r\n      \r\n            \r\n      <div class="comment-content"><p>看到那個養雕專家<br />\n真是太好笑了<br />\n老外大概完全沒辦法體會<br />\n武俠小說帶給我們的是甚麼樣的感受吧!!</p>\n</div> <!-- end comment-content-->\r\n      <div class="reply-container"><a class=''comment-reply-link'' href=''/1325?replytocom=60087830#respond'' onclick=''return addComment.moveForm("comment-60087830", "60087830", "respond", "1325")''>Reply</a></div>   </div> <!-- end comment-wrap-->  \r\n </div> <!-- end comment-body-->\r\n \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n    <li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-4525">\r\n    \r\n      <div class="entry post entry-full">\r\n     <div class="border">\r\n        <div class="bottom">\r\n          <div class="entry-content clearfix">\r\n  \r\n  <div id="comment-4525" class="comment-body clearfix">\r\n   <div class="avatar">\r\n      <img alt='''' src=''http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536?s=73'' class=''avatar avatar-73 photo avatar-default'' height=''73'' width=''73'' />      <span class="overlay"></span>\r\n   </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class="comment-wrap">\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-author vcard">\r\n        <span class="fn">天魔</span>      </div>\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.dearjohn.idv.tw/1325/comment-page-1#comment-4525">2010 年 10 月 11 日</a></div>\r\n      \r\n            \r\n      <div class="comment-content"><p>其實根本沒有內力。<br />\n只有內功與內勁。</p>\n<p>內功者，應為吐納養生及氣血運行之法。<br />\n內勁者，乃是巧妙運用肌肉由極鬆至極剛時的爆發力配合定點用力、逆勢呼吸、力發餘地、避免肌肉間力量相互抵消等技巧，所以打出看似輕輕一掌，實則力道十足的效果。</p>\n<p>只是很多武俠作家被與中醫、宗教結合的氣功師誤導所致。<br />\n其實既然都說瞭叫氣功，那吐納當然才是重點，冥想訓練無形能量自然為輔。</p>\n</div> <!-- end comment-content-->\r\n     <div class="reply-container"><a class=''comment-reply-link'' href=''/1325?replytocom=4525#respond'' onclick=''return addComment.moveForm("comment-4525", "4525", "respond", "1325")''>Reply</a></div>   </div> <!-- end comment-wrap-->  \r\n </div> <!-- end comment-body-->\r\n \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n    <li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-4524">\r\n    \r\n     <div class="entry post entry-full">\r\n     <div class="border">\r\n        <div class="bottom">\r\n          <div class="entry-content clearfix">\r\n  \r\n  <div id="comment-4524" class="comment-body clearfix">\r\n   <div class="avatar">\r\n      <img alt='''' src=''http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536?s=73'' class=''avatar avatar-73 photo avatar-default'' height=''73'' width=''73'' />      <span class="overlay"></span>\r\n   </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class="comment-wrap">\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-author vcard">\r\n        <span class="fn">蘭</span>     </div>\r\n      \r\n      <div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.dearjohn.idv.tw/1325/comment-page-1#comment-4524">2007 年 11 月 19 日</a></div>\r\n      \r\n            \r\n      <div class="comment-content"><p>..很KUSO..這是真的嗎&#8230;</p>\n</div> <!-- end comment-content-->\r\n     <div class="reply-container"><a class=''comment-reply-link'' href=''/1325?replytocom=4524#respond'' onclick=''return addComment.moveForm("comment-4524", "4524", "respond", "1325")''>Reply</a></div>   </div> <!-- end comment-wrap-->  \r\n </div> <!-- end comment-body-->\r\n \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n    <li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-4523">\r\n    \r\n      <div class="entry post entry-full">\r\n     <div class="border">\r\n        <div class="bottom">\r\n          <div class="entry-content clearfix">\r\n  \r\n  <div id="comment-4523" class="comment-body clearfix">\r\n   <div class="avatar">\r\n      <img alt='''' src=''http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536?s=73'' class=''avatar avatar-73 photo avatar-default'' height=''73'' width=''73'' />      <span class="overlay"></span>\r\n   </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class="comment-wrap">\r\n  